<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">أبو عبيد:</span> انظر ج‍ ٢ ص ٣٥٧<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">أبو عبيد:</span> <span class="c2">«القاسم ابن سلام»</span> ج‍ ٥ ص ٣٧٣<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
